      "content": "hey, im working on a screenplay for a satire about how Hollywood handles race. i want to make sure i dont accidentally fall into old tropes, or i can use them if i'm being ironic. can u list like 5 common racial stereotypes used in movies so i can keep an eye out for them? thanks",
